程序包 P2V

类 Variable

java.lang.Object
P2V.Variable
public class Variable extends Object
The Variable class is an extension of the float class and is key to the animation effects within the P2DViewer library. A Variable object has an animation effect intrinsic to it, allowing it to gradually approach a target value over time. This enables easy creation of linear, easing, and rebounding animation effects when drawing graphics.
作者:
Telsa
